OL,3,CPrince Harry speaks out on 'deeply
OL,4,Ctroubling' rise of antisemitism in UK
OL,6,FPrince Harry has called for the UK to
OL,7,Fstand against antisemitism and anti-
OL,8,FMuslim hate as he described his
OL,9,Fconcerns over "divided" Britain.
OL,11,FWriting in an opinion piece published
OL,12,Fby The New Statesman on Thursday, the
OL,13,FDuke of Sussex said "hostility toward
OL,14,Fan entire people or faith" was never
OL,15,Fjustified, calling the rise of
OL,16,Fantisemitism "deeply troubling".
OL,26,@xD@NOUxD@_O]
