OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778785872
OL,3,CPrince Harry speaks out on 'deeply
OL,4,Ctroubling' rise of antisemitism in UK
OL,6,FReferencing recent "lethal violence"
OL,7,Fagainst the Jewish community in London
OL,8,Fand Manchester, Harry said "hatred
OL,9,Fdirected at people for who they are,
OL,10,For what they believe" was not protest
OL,11,Fbut "prejudice" in action.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@TOUnD@dO]pD@\OU
