PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1778785872
OL,3,CPrince Harry speaks out on 'deeply
OL,4,Ctroubling' rise of antisemitism in UK
OL,6,F"We cannot ignore a difficult truth:
OL,7,Fwhen states act without
OL,8,Faccountability, and in ways that raise
OL,9,Fserious questions under international
OL,10,Fhumanitarian law ` criticism is both
OL,11,Flegitimate, necessary and essential in
OL,12,Fany democracy," Harry said.
OL,14,F"The consequences do not remain
OL,15,Fcontained within borders. They
OL,16,Freverberate outward, shaping
OL,17,Fperception, inflaming tensions."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
