OL,3,CPrince Harry speaks out on 'deeply
OL,4,Ctroubling' rise of antisemitism in UK
OL,6,FHarry also said he had learned from
OL,7,Fhis own "past mistakes", having been
OL,8,Fphotographed wearing a Nazi uniform to
OL,9,Fa party in January 2005, at the age of
OL,10,F20.
OL,12,FClarence House said Harry apologised
OL,13,Ffor the "poor choice of costume" at
OL,14,Fthe time, which the Board of Deputies
OL,15,Fof British Jews said the costume was
OL,16,Fin "bad taste".
OL,26,@oD@IOUoD@WO]
