OL,3,CPrince Harry speaks out on 'deeply
OL,4,Ctroubling' rise of antisemitism in UK
OL,6,FHarry concluded his piece with an
OL,7,Fappeal for "unity" and a call for
OL,8,Fpeople to stand against antisemitism
OL,9,Fand anti-Muslim hate "wherever it
OL,10,Fappears".
OL,12,F"When anger is turned towards
OL,13,Fcommunities ` whether Jewish, Muslim,
OL,14,For any other ` it ceases to be a call
OL,15,Ffor justice and becomes something far
OL,16,Fmore corrosive," he wrote.
OL,26,@oD@LOUoD@RO]qD@VOUrD@HO]tD@AOUxD@PO]
