OL,3,CPrince Harry speaks out on 'deeply
OL,4,Ctroubling' rise of antisemitism in UK
OL,6,FHarry's words come amid a series of
OL,7,Farson attacks at Jewish sites in
OL,8,FLondon since March, as well as a
OL,9,Fdouble stabbing in Golders Green that
OL,10,Fis being treated as an act of
OL,11,Fterrorism.
OL,13,FEssa Suleiman is accused of stabbing
OL,14,Ftwo Jewish men in Golders Green, north
OL,15,FLondon, on April 29, after attacking a
OL,16,FMuslim man at a home in Southwark
OL,17,Fearlier the same day.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
