OL,3,CPrince Harry speaks out on 'deeply
OL,4,Ctroubling' rise of antisemitism in UK
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police deployed 100
OL,7,Fextra officers to help safeguard the
OL,8,FJewish community across the capital
OL,9,Fthis month.
OL,11,FThe patrols cover areas with large
OL,12,FJewish populations, like Golders
OL,13,FGreen, Hendon, Finchley and Edgware,
OL,14,Fand only respond to reports of terror
OL,15,Fattacks and hate crimes.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
